    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/c4f8e25a9316be43d2957c78b0872250.poster.avif?t=1759204261\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/c4f8e25a9316be43d2957c78b0872250.webm?t=1759204261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《狩夜人》是一款复古风动作冒险游戏，兼具快节奏、重技巧的玩法与深邃的暗黑幻想情节。玩家将扮演维斯珀——一位高洁的“逐影者”，徜徉于布满断壁残垣与怖怪之物的迈德拉世界。深入强敌盘踞的地下城，挑战难以攻陷的boss，灵活运用多种武器与暗夜之力，为人类夺回夜晚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/972a5e520b7ac6064576ec8be1361666.poster.avif?t=1759204261\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/972a5e520b7ac6064576ec8be1361666.webm?t=1759204261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/972a5e520b7ac6064576ec8be1361666.mp4?t=1759204261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是人类文明的第9纪。白天，世界处于人类治下，而夜晚则由诸多可怖之物主宰。无论人类如何抵抗，每当夜幕降临便会迎来一次灭顶之灾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一群自称“逐影者”的人类发现了驾驭暗夜之力的方法，继而学会了如何武装自己、对抗黑夜。然而，他们的力量仍不足以扭转局势。每当黎明到来，人类在东山再起的同时，仍抱有这样一个绝望的念头：夜幕的降临，即是毁灭的前奏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此时，人类发现了“夜之圣印”——能够终止昼夜循环、令白昼永远持续的圣物。逐影者们自愿立下血誓，令太阳普照千年；对人类来说，希望从未如此光芒万丈。然而，命运无可违逆，人类终究要为这一切付出代价。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如今，最后一缕光明也被黑夜吞没。作为名正言顺的逐影者，背叛者的女儿维斯珀将游历垂死的大地，挽回人类文明的余烬。这是一场与命运赛跑的狩猎行动；夜的黑影不仅吞噬着大地，也侵染着她的心智。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/00d4f6a29464035759dbddebb9fee696.poster.avif?t=1759204261\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/00d4f6a29464035759dbddebb9fee696.webm?t=1759204261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/00d4f6a29464035759dbddebb9fee696.mp4?t=1759204261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/4731dc82e5a25d5199257c1ba63fba42.avif?t=1759204261\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >施放连续技的同时冲锋陷阵，或挥舞兵器，或释放暗夜之力，一骑当千。玩家可在近战与远程攻击之间快速切换：比如，用刀剑斩击敌人后立刻冲刺拉开距离、使用远程武器，将攻击悉数闪避。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/2e16b32c4ba6168835a3f1bdac95c60b.avif?t=1759204261\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与无数次毁灭人类的古老夜之妖魔交战，在惊心动魄的boss战中迎接最高难度的挑战。寻找弱点、摸清攻击模式，逐步突破难度与刺激程度层层递进的多阶段战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/c4f0287b4f524930632c9e271842f4d2.avif?t=1759204261\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或依据玩家自己的游戏习惯，或针对某些特定的boss，主人公的战斗风格支持随意打造。玩家可在多种多样的升级项目中自由选择，并选择最适合自己游戏风格的装备，从暴击、生命窃取，到毒攻、近战、火力压制，玩法流派不一而足。收集血瓶、鸦羽、月石与宵铁，提升各项属性，在黑夜面前武装自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/34dad995347250609420c62b9644fe09.avif?t=1759204261\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以动作冒险的形式探索迈德拉的黑暗幻想世界，闯过满是陷阱、敌人、谜题与挑战的地下城，从古老教堂到留存失传知识的图书馆，发现各类地点，了解其中失落王国与分崩离析的漂浮城市的奥秘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/b73357a16f33bbd9bec1647e7112152e.avif?t=1759204261\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >于“鸦巢”接受任务，狩猎暗夜凶兽。找出它们的藏身地，将最强大的夜之生灵悉数击倒。每完成一次狩猎，你都将获得报酬，令生命值与暗夜之力逐渐增长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/3c98a4b81502bd40ab28ef80b9dded3e.avif?t=1759204261\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >漫游毁灭边缘的世界，同形形色色的角色相遇，了解他们各自的悲壮人生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649740/extras/68d19add3e901f0694d1d80fe83aadb6.avif?t=1759204261\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随游戏进程、boss对手与所在地点变化的沉浸式自适应背景音乐，与《圣剑传说2》作曲家菊田裕树联合创作。</p>",
